snippet.description:
Special thanks to Nintendo for sending us a code for the game!

We've only just started exploring the new levels in Super Mario Maker 2! There are so many great creators - we could go on HOURS! Today we are going to try to beat some of the HARDEST levels as well as ones submitted by you all in our last Mario Maker 2 episode!

Watch us BEAT The New Ross Mario Maker 2 level! ► https://bit.ly/2XlV6iz

Find the game here ► https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/super-mario-maker-2-switch/

Levels We Played Today:
Look Cool? Feel Cool! by JirardTOVG - W0B-P7P-6SG
Do You Trust Me? by JirardTOVG - K9M-235-0LG
The Pits of Finland by Eddiember - HJM-8WN-9PG
Chompers On Ice by MakerMoris - 7L2-QYW-STG
Game Theory by Person101 - W4G-N46-1HG
Intriguing Title (kill red fish) by Egtlive - T99-L3J-DVG
